The &quot;not talking&quot; part is basically just there to help you stick to the code of discipline [1] which is:<p>1. to abstain from killing any being;
2. to abstain from stealing;
3. to abstain from all sexual activity;
4. to abstain from telling lies;
5. to abstain from all intoxicants.<p>With &quot;not talking&quot; you automatically follow number 4 :)<p>[1] <a href="https://www.dhamma.org/en/about/code" rel="nofollow">https://www.dhamma.org/en/about/code</a>
